N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5106.3 - Vendor license application and disclosure form

State Regulations

Each applicant for a video lottery gaming vendor license
will be required to submit a vendor license application in such form prescribed
by the commission. Notes
